    <sect2 id="Qore_File_printf">
      <title>File::printf()</title>
      
     <variablelist>
	<varlistentry>
	  <term>Synopsis</term>
	  <listitem>
	    <para>Writes a formatted string with soft field widths to the file.  See <link linkend="Qore_File_f_printf">File::f_printf()</link> for a similar method that enforces field widths.  See <link linkend="String_Formatting">String Formatting</link> for more information about the format string.</para>
